name: Jake Metcalf
coverLetter: Been trimming for 5 years and can trim a pound or more daily. Traveling with 2 girls who also need work but are not as experienced (real nice to look at though) have own car, tent, and shears and are hardworking, honest and respectable, nice people. No aggro types or drama here 👍👍👍 just need some work to keep us moving in our travels.
